{"tid":2374243,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"咁既時勢，我越黎越覺得出貓都係實力既一種。","createTime":"2021-01-21T05:40:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T05:55:03.000Z","uid":94266,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ff16d033ed4998d1a7aae1d43d1e7466818a706d","tid":2374243,"uid":94266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:40:52.000Z","msg":"係，出貓係唔啱，我認同。<br />\n出貓畀人捉到係垃圾，<br />\n但成功到，就係實力一種，<br />\n因為呢個世界本身就唔公平，你睇吓新聞。<br />\n不過，唔好誤會，我唔係鼓勵大家出貓，亦都唔係鼓勵大家做大奸大惡，我只係覺得出到貓都係實力既一種，同時，做人太過忠忠直直，終需乞食。"},{"pid":"28a993fe1bc269ee27d08c717e8c9c08c2f7aa84","tid":2374243,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:45:08.000Z","msg":"美國總統都出貓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b2ff4a89f2e9640f57600b96ae63999a4b5da3","tid":2374243,"uid":100016,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:46:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bab75e08eaee7cabf438ad75c007d303e2472e24","tid":2374243,"uid":357040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:53:49.000Z","msg":"兒登"},{"pid":"8b5d02601ca4a72021cb58b0dbd4c7152738c27a","tid":2374243,"uid":161767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:54:21.000Z","msg":"唔俾人發現就係"},{"pid":"ba044e6b3ad052a855a5f4ba13a90c08b73e983a","tid":2374243,"uid":374353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:54:21.000Z","msg":"你當自己考緊中忍考試?"},{"pid":"ff96135a7f36bbc764c05b7b0ae42492f2ff0bc9","tid":2374243,"uid":210161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:55:03.000Z","msg":"小學已覺得"}]}